6c6db42d8b41d2","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菜+蕃薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蕃薯唔係好似好肥嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高糖高澱粉質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568e78544f6d125b497d62c98b38a6dbd2784db7","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豆腐肉碎西蘭花<br />\n薯仔低脂芝士肉碎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好食咁,用咩調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小小鹽</blockquote><br />\n好唔好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465723cb05587ce62c74c4e4a4612ce9419faa35","tid":222722,"uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"睇見都唔想食"},{"pid":"6b650c4c1c6ec079843aefe63c1150f93002dd45","tid":222722,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:02:55.000Z","msg":"18件麥樂雞餐加大<br />\n利申 日日游水"},{"pid":"1491449a20fa10a844af38d066a295fc957f0d3f","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇見都唔想食</blockquote><br />\n咁你想食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930097e6f6fde7fb80c88193074ce2f30ae6b6ba","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>18件麥樂雞餐加大<br />\n利申 日日游水</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ae6f05ade279b9f42bb59f31ba49859407413d","tid":222722,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇做運動</blockquote><br />\n一星期1~3次1小時跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放工返到屋企已經攰到唔想郁"},{"pid":"416b0feab808930f33472a11ed7d6bdda434371d","tid":222722,"uid":93436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:07:10.000Z","msg":"試過福字米粉加靜熱水 零味精湯粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n生菜+蕃茄+青瓜+粟米 +日式柚子汁+檸檬汁<br />\n可以加下小油煎雞胸或者三文魚之類 唔會肥得去邊<br />\n菜食幾多都唔肥 食到飽"},{"pid":"f0087a3004b82ece473f9fce7c26e37182893f33","tid":222722,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>豆腐番茄粟米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n煲埋一齊?咩玩法............<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好食，類似番茄蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n求煮法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係亂煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係切好番茄豆腐，之後落水，蕃茄豆腐同一粒粒嘅粟米<br />\n調味就隨心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7c09f25c0da56f5420c873849100735ef6d95d","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇做運動</blockquote><br />\n一星期1~3次1小時跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放工返到屋企已經攰到唔想郁</blockquote><br />\n所以有時我都係一星座做到一次咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dd2798bbdc316f611f75f1572fa33ee62db4a1","tid":222722,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豆腐肉碎西蘭花<br />\n薯仔低脂芝士肉碎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好食咁,用咩調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小小鹽</blockquote><br />\n好唔好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實薯仔個個幾好味，豆腐西蘭花就冇味，要加少少豉油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9152643d3ff5b9a3cc8f4b62b8a1fe8ffff38c","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過福字米粉加靜熱水 零味精湯粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n生菜+蕃茄+青瓜+粟米 +日式柚子汁+檸檬汁<br />\n可以加下小油煎雞胸或者三文魚之類 唔會肥得去邊<br />\n菜食幾多都唔肥 食到飽</blockquote><br />\n柚子係西柚?日式係邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2170d7ff2c20af037ff18ae48e894507c7f548","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:12:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豆腐肉碎西蘭花<br />\n薯仔低脂芝士肉碎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好食咁,用咩調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小小鹽</blockquote><br />\n好唔好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實薯仔個個幾好味，豆腐西蘭花就冇味，要加少少豉油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我偷師學藝先,多謝師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70e10f50ec891365cd2dae4d11df6b5e689cc70","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇做運動</blockquote><br />\n一星期1~3次1小時跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放工返到屋企已經攰到唔想郁</blockquote><br />\n所以有時我都係一星<span style=\"color: red;\">座</span>做到一次咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n期"},{"pid":"ce4a49dcd88d0b898ed43a946e07c34ddbc36241","tid":222722,"uid":93436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過福字米粉加靜熱水 零味精湯粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n生菜+蕃茄+青瓜+粟米 +日式柚子汁+檸檬汁<br />\n可以加下小油煎雞胸或者三文魚之類 唔會肥得去邊<br />\n菜食幾多都唔肥 食到飽</blockquote><br />\n柚子係西柚?日式係邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係一田買到既日式柚子汁 日式醬汁??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識形容係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但睇個成份表卡路里 糖份都唔高<br />\n加落沙律酸酸甜甜幾香<br />\n<br />\nBtw餃子個類野好高卡路里唔好食太多啦"},{"pid":"2fb69ab3f5ab31cf0b43b13a789ff1f174a397c9","tid":222722,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:18:01.000Z","msg":"我之前食得太清，減到好辛苦。<br />\n之後會冇恆心，所以宜家都開始唔食太清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c00b2345418df34c39f0bb1ae8089ecb487a42","tid":222722,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:22:07.000Z","msg":"留名待煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3769917765494798ae228c5c94ea8d1773179dd2","tid":222722,"uid":13512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:26:29.000Z","msg":"On9，餃子好撚肥，豆腐好高熱量，番薯薯仔飯呢啲澱粉質多，咁點減肥，其實油鹽糖少啲做下運動已經好好，注意飯量同飲食時間同頻率更有效"},{"pid":"802e634c53e442ff44a8fb2e72cd1885531e93cf","tid":222722,"uid":23720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:34:58.000Z","msg":"餃子好肥食少啲<br />\n另外嗰個瓜黎？<br />\n可以烚/少油煎雞胸食"},{"pid":"0abfe0542e0ced71077e9a7773e3d2fd23815c1d","tid":222722,"uid":55792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:36:39.000Z","msg":"早餐<br />\nmanuka honey+牛油果+chia seeds三文治"},{"pid":"65bd3a75dcb93b860ced010bb3f3803d33d12c84","tid":222722,"uid":29485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg&h=2e46186f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n下好正wor 節瓜烚蛋水餃"},{"pid":"c5c2ed8f534d82e59ab04df6f594664b93a17b00","tid":222722,"uid":62517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T19:13:35.000Z","msg":"麥皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ced99afb94e0eb6a2f29698464c75c2626d053","tid":222722,"uid":67816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T19:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>菜+蕃薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蕃薯唔係好似好肥嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高糖高澱粉質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網睇話食蕃薯好過食飯 唔知真唔真<br />\n我都係間唔中用蕃薯黎代替飯<br />\n唔食澱粉質好似成日都肚餓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d8fcf397f0a322efb139ccbb53fb41bf3b8380","tid":222722,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T19:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg&h=2e46186f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n水餃好多調味料  減肥唔好食"},{"pid":"068f6e72617f93b23b59bdd85d722cc93e3483b9","tid":222722,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T02:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9，餃子好撚肥，豆腐好高熱量，番薯薯仔飯呢啲澱粉質多，咁點減肥，其實油鹽糖少啲做下運動已經好好，注意飯量同飲食時間同頻率更有效</blockquote><br />\n 凡事都要適量，控制分量就得。唔食澱粉會冇能量，個人會變遲鈍。薯仔卡路里比起飯低，而且仲容易飽肚。其實薯仔同番薯凍食澱粉質會減半。<br />\n豆腐補充蛋白質，冇肉類咁多脂肪。同等分類嘅蛋白質會較多。而且女仔減肥最好要食豆腐，豆漿。如果唔係會減埋個胸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df8fb2d3fc17534dd4f0faf96d868c98e5d91cb","tid":222722,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg&h=2e46186f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n個水餃是韓國餃子？營養師都推介個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed97c17358e5d1ad6fb8ae24e07d736937105be0","tid":222722,"uid":73910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"我戒糖戒凍飲戒零食，間中跑步踩單車，減左5kg"},{"pid":"5287d0b076876c8928b8e61b24be267f70855ef1","tid":222722,"uid":2093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"屋企煎塊三文魚，恰碗菜，加碗紅米飯又一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b65ef68938a39f1a3e81a481986810631edc523","tid":222722,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食蕉   已經個半月</blockquote><br />\n餐餐食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工日子  早餐晚餐都係一隻蕉    午餐要同同事有交流，通常叫粉麵少麵  再食剩少少</blockquote><br />\n聽講唔可以食太多,蕉的糖份好多,好致肥,而且唔夠某d營養好似會仲難減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你將平時食開既野食一半就停唔洗戒口得閑跑下步咁就一定減到我用呢個方法十個月減六十磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80cba97d9b1eb26ce7e70561611d3ada4ae751d","tid":222722,"uid":92194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"早餐<br />\n麥皮<br />\n蘋果一個<br />\n橙一個<br />\n<br />\n午餐<br />\n墨丸米<br />\n油菜一碟<br />\n<br />\n晚餐<br />\n泡菜雜菌豆腐湯<br />\n蒸魚/煎魚<br />\n飯3/4碗<br />\n<br />\n最緊要做運動"},{"pid":"86b643575724caa63a19a6dec00a94b7ee1ef2a9","tid":222722,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:46:07.000Z","msg":"早餐 叮叮肉醬意<br />\n午餐 滑強炸雞扒飯<br />\n晚餐 double滑強炸雞扒飯<br />\n甜品 朱古力餅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef1cb34e502465d267ddffe9cde8c925117c848","tid":222722,"uid":968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:17:42.000Z","msg":"其實點食都無所謂 <br />\n最緊要係運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51a16bc9762c776c65beb8fdc1e175412463bfc","tid":222722,"uid":2093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點食都無所謂 <br />\n最緊要係運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔戒口，做幾多運動都冇用"},{"pid":"f61dd70727c28b72ca6a93635b51b2855a104cd3","tid":222722,"uid":107425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"我咩都照食 <br />\n但我4月跟8-9小時食野法<br />\n係8-9小時內完成三餐 之後時間飲水<br />\n肚腩細左啲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1bd5455ac7cad7f6ec8b19f796cf5e26ad667c","tid":222722,"uid":59165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:28:13.000Z","msg":"話蕃薯好肥個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蕃薯係好高纖維 減肥餐食量小左吸收營養小左好易便秘<br />\n其實食夠基礎代謝率加d運動就得 唔好過多"},{"pid":"eca56fc81131e0c3049323f7f1edd86c6ceca4ea","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg&h=2e46186f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n個水餃是韓國餃子？營養師都推介個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係..不過我唔係營養師推介,我係超市自己發現,試左好多款口味了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7755bb665fac9385a4de6032d6f997521e55dc07","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我戒糖戒凍飲戒零食，間中跑步踩單車，減左5kg</blockquote><br />\n我已經減左3kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c876e97b1fbbbcdd234a0afb484dfa01b06442f","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企煎塊三文魚，恰碗菜，加碗紅米飯又一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾好,不過我唔識煎魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c569a84e1097df6d54890dbc49db1d0a3cf35e","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食蕉   已經個半月</blockquote><br />\n餐餐食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工日子  早餐晚餐都係一隻蕉    午餐要同同事有交流，通常叫粉麵少麵  再食剩少少</blockquote><br />\n聽講唔可以食太多,蕉的糖份好多,好致肥,而且唔夠某d營養好似會仲難減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你將平時食開既野食一半就停唔洗戒口得閑跑下步咁就一定減到我用呢個方法十個月減六十磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食一半會心癢癢而且唔飽肚會想再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我寧願食齋d 唔過個卡路里所需,<br />\n咁應該可以減到掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38aa7839d20bd7599ba73f1dfc7c6db1ad97efb7","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早餐 叮叮肉醬意<br />\n午餐 滑強炸雞扒飯<br />\n晚餐 double滑強炸雞扒飯<br />\n甜品 朱古力餅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自殺餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2ae169416c4723480a12cc9054de1fb8bdb358","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點食都無所謂 <br />\n最緊要係運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲食配合都好重要!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5979963955f3a2a51dea9e3c75bab59e5445791","tid":222722,"uid":94029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"我減肥嗰陣通常一餐食烚雞胸2～3舊，一粒烚蛋，半份三文治(全麥方包+蕃茄+青瓜)<br />\n晚餐多數食冬瓜湯/蕃茄雜菜湯煮麥片<br />\n配合每日兩個鐘有氧運動"},{"pid":"83175bba8266483022a30035beaae37c65a06a99","tid":222722,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg&h=2e46186f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n個水餃是韓國餃子？營養師都推介個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係..不過我唔係營養師推介,我係超市自己發現,試左好多款口味了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係上網睇，不過原來有韭菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5616c36eed26c3fc20bafa1b44d93bff2ffbfe64","tid":222722,"uid":5866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實點食都無所謂 <br />\n最緊要係運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲食配合都好重要!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但都要注意基礎代謝<br />\n你食唔夠最低熱量啫係節食減肥<br />\n好易反彈"},{"pid":"dcfc41f1612540fa80cc7c9923609cb6bde9dc70","tid":222722,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食蕉   已經個半月</blockquote><br />\n餐餐食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工日子  早餐晚餐都係一隻蕉    午餐要同同事有交流，通常叫粉麵少麵  再食剩少少</blockquote><br />\n聽講唔可以食太多,蕉的糖份好多,好致肥,而且唔夠某d營養好似會仲難減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你將平時食開既野食一半就停唔洗戒口得閑跑下步咁就一定減到我用呢個方法十個月減六十磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食一半會心癢癢而且唔飽肚會想再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我寧願食齋d 唔過個卡路里所需,<br />\n咁應該可以減到掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你咪減唔到肥囉死肥婆賣玻蘿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9104148942c8308fbde161f93372bb866434ce","tid":222722,"uid":3272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"試過每餐食少D，但好快肚餓，餓到胃痛，點好"},{"pid":"65e8abd471fbc88a54bf710bbbabdc67510da505","tid":222722,"uid":5866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食蕉   已經個半月</blockquote><br />\n餐餐食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工日子  早餐晚餐都係一隻蕉    午餐要同同事有交流，通常叫粉麵少麵  再食剩少少</blockquote><br />\n聽講唔可以食太多,<span style=\"color: purple;\">蕉的糖份好多,好致肥</span>,而且唔夠某d營養好似會仲難減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e99d85a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&h=9c501e89\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香蕉一直被很多人視為減肥聖品，日本有一位腸道科權威也建議大家在晚餐半小時前吃兩根香蕉，並搭配200CC的水，10天內能瘦3公斤</span>。國內營養師解釋<span style=\"color: gold;\">香蕉能快速補充糖分，飢餓感就會降低，的確有助減肥</span>，不過還是要適量，尤其腎臟功能不好的民眾不要吃太多。<br />\n<br />\n糖分高=/=致肥"},{"pid":"43ba8597060af15e4eeeefff40fb70aabf5a2749","tid":222722,"uid":25107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:22:16.000Z","msg":"試過7月75kg 做運動+控制飲食 9月63kg <br />\n蕃薯 菜 生果 雞"},{"pid":"97bdeb96aece5711869758de706cec4610b8afae","tid":222722,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:28:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我戒糖戒凍飲戒零食，間中跑步踩單車，減左5kg</blockquote><br />\n減過60磅"},{"pid":"f63b3c433db7f1c0472014c2e7fbef26185f8362","tid":222722,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食蕉   已經個半月</blockquote><br />\n餐餐食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工日子  早餐晚餐都係一隻蕉    午餐要同同事有交流，通常叫粉麵少麵  再食剩少少</blockquote><br />\n聽講唔可以食太多,<span style=\"color: purple;\">蕉的糖份好多,好致肥</span>,而且唔夠某d營養好似會仲難減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e99d85a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&h=9c501e89\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香蕉一直被很多人視為減肥聖品，日本有一位腸道科權威也建議大家在晚餐半小時前吃兩根香蕉，並搭配200CC的水，10天內能瘦3公斤</span>。國內營養師解釋<span style=\"color: gold;\">香蕉能快速補充糖分，飢餓感就會降低，的確有助減肥</span>，不過還是要適量，尤其腎臟功能不好的民眾不要吃太多。<br />\n<br />\n糖分高=/=致肥</blockquote><br />\n高GI就易肥"},{"pid":"31a6bcbfdc82fb535af26ecad464f6882e139c18","tid":222722,"uid":103440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e90afa233776c48bd9532d34b6fb272d66243a3","tid":222722,"uid":1870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/225225_d16ee451e5350b33225a82f465f6a74a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F225225_d16ee451e5350b33225a82f465f6a74a.jpg&h=6bc5be28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33274c9303ab0e015ac4844484b7a7876bc268eb","tid":222722,"uid":97515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T00:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食蕉   已經個半月</blockquote><br />\n餐餐食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工日子  早餐晚餐都係一隻蕉    午餐要同同事有交流，通常叫粉麵少麵  再食剩少少</blockquote><br />\n聽講唔可以食太多,<span style=\"color: purple;\">蕉的糖份好多,好致肥</span>,而且唔夠某d營養好似會仲難減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e99d85a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&h=9c501e89\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香蕉一直被很多人視為減肥聖品，日本有一位腸道科權威也建議大家在晚餐半小時前吃兩根香蕉，並搭配200CC的水，10天內能瘦3公斤</span>。國內營養師解釋<span style=\"color: gold;\">香蕉能快速補充糖分，飢餓感就會降低，的確有助減肥</span>，不過還是要適量，尤其腎臟功能不好的民眾不要吃太多。<br />\n<br />\n糖分高=/=致肥</blockquote><br />\n高GI就易肥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係蕉真係有飽肚感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又方便帶同食，收工食一隻，直接去gym room做運動"},{"pid":"2b6f4d4f5dd74a7c0ddfaffc53103e80c1056911","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T00:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌劣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F013849_0b06735153786602f5616f1ee32b6264.jpg&h=2e46186f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n個水餃是韓國餃子？營養師都推介個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係..不過我唔係營養師推介,我係超市自己發現,試左好多款口味了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係上網睇，不過原來有韭菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜有韭菜咩..睇過好多間唔覺有咁嘅,下次再留心望下先,好鐘意韭菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596f4e9a68d812ae0b4d1139ef19ce37fe17064e","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T00:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食蕉   已經個半月</blockquote><br />\n餐餐食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工日子  早餐晚餐都係一隻蕉    午餐要同同事有交流，通常叫粉麵少麵  再食剩少少</blockquote><br />\n聽講唔可以食太多,蕉的糖份好多,好致肥,而且唔夠某d營養好似會仲難減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你將平時食開既野食一半就停唔洗戒口得閑跑下步咁就一定減到我用呢個方法十個月減六十磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食一半會心癢癢而且唔飽肚會想再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我寧願食齋d 唔過個卡路里所需,<br />\n咁應該可以減到掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你咪減唔到肥囉死肥婆賣<span style=\"color: red;\">玻</span>蘿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 菠蘿呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔想賣!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以好努力減左3kg了,有d慢,但希望唔會反彈就好,我驚食蕉會餓親反彈#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb0eba03b7b8b2cd5258afee253c5d09f8b5cb1","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T00:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過每餐食少D，但好快肚餓，餓到胃痛，點好</blockquote><br />\n所以唔好唔食而減,我係食到飽每餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過計好曬唔過自己所需吸收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9727f5c229dfe1a1dca5b165a83af661d1988225","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T00:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過7月75kg 做運動+控制飲食 9月63kg <br />\n蕃薯 菜 生果 雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊加油"},{"pid":"fd034ce72c99f8f582957cf32b007e7fc5be36d1","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T00:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒所有糖份飲品，零食<br />\n一餐只食面包同代餐粉<br />\n正餐食清淡 多菜少肉</blockquote><br />\n面包咪仲肥....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 精製澱粉質喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54c195193ea7be6e91fd1a51d092cd7da170514","tid":222722,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T00:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食蕉   已經個半月</blockquote><br />\n餐餐食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工日子  早餐晚餐都係一隻蕉    午餐要同同事有交流，通常叫粉麵少麵  再食剩少少</blockquote><br />\n聽講唔可以食太多,<span style=\"color: purple;\">蕉的糖份好多,好致肥</span>,而且唔夠某d營養好似會仲難減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e99d85a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&h=9c501e89\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香蕉一直被很多人視為減肥聖品，日本有一位腸道科權威也建議大家在晚餐半小時前吃兩根香蕉，並搭配200CC的水，10天內能瘦3公斤</span>。國內營養師解釋<span style=\"color: gold;\">香蕉能快速補充糖分，飢餓感就會降低，的確有助減肥</span>，不過還是要適量，尤其腎臟功能不好的民眾不要吃太多。<br />\n<br />\n糖分高=/=致肥</blockquote><br />\n高GI就易肥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係蕉真係有飽肚感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又方便帶同食，收工食一隻，直接去gym room做運動</blockquote><br />\n之後唔會餓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93e4b2ae1e30852c0ccfe22d68218093634c356","tid":222722,"uid":97515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T00:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食蕉   已經個半月</blockquote><br />\n餐餐食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工日子  早餐晚餐都係一隻蕉    午餐要同同事有交流，通常叫粉麵少麵  再食剩少少</blockquote><br />\n聽講唔可以食太多,<span style=\"color: purple;\">蕉的糖份好多,好致肥</span>,而且唔夠某d營養好似會仲難減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e99d85a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D111682&h=9c501e89\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=111682</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香蕉一直被很多人視為減肥聖品，日本有一位腸道科權威也建議大家在晚餐半小時前吃兩根香蕉，並搭配200CC的水，10天內能瘦3公斤</span>。國內營養師解釋<span style=\"color: gold;\">香蕉能快速補充糖分，飢餓感就會降低，的確有助減肥</span>，不過還是要適量，尤其腎臟功能不好的民眾不要吃太多。<br />\n<br />\n糖分高=/=致肥</blockquote><br />\n高GI就易肥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係蕉真係有飽肚感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又方便帶同食，收工食一隻，直接去gym room做運動</blockquote><br />\n之後唔會餓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分散注意力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做緊運動果陣唔覺餓<br />\n做完返到屋企都10點幾，沖個涼執下野就訓"},{"pid":"dd2abbbfa2c7e7eb17087dba39469eac5b27856d","tid":222722,"uid":25107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過7月75kg 做運動+控制飲食 9月63kg <br />\n蕃薯 菜 生果 雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊加油</blockquote><br />\n依家57 lu 開始做gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef25a6ba5a7487f875ed02cfda85204546744c9","tid":222722,"uid":26969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9，餃子好撚肥，豆腐好高熱量，番薯薯仔飯呢啲澱粉質多，咁點減肥，其實油鹽糖少啲做下運動已經好好，注意飯量同飲食時間同頻率更有效</blockquote><br />\n餃子如果買既話買惠康買CJ 個隻睇返營養標籤係OKAY 的， 當然可以就自己包，我會瘦肉或雞肉加冬菇加菜做餡<br />\n同埋澱粉質點都要食架 咩叫均衡飲食<br />\n適當咁食就可以